<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,417,910]" pageId="6" pageNumber="511">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,610,453,478]" pageId="6" pageNumber="511">
Condition of the 
<typeStatus box="[406,470,453,478]" pageId="6" pageNumber="511">types</typeStatus>
. 
<typeStatus box="[484,605,453,478]" pageId="6" pageNumber="511">Lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
Forewings rubbed, left hindwing slightly damaged. Part of the antennal pectinations damaged. Most legs missing. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[626,798,489,514]" pageId="6" pageNumber="511">
<typeStatus box="[626,793,489,514]" pageId="6" pageNumber="511">Paralectotype</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
Almost all legs missing, and wings badly rubbed.
</paragraph>
